Daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya karu da sauri a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya.
Ƙididdigar ƙaruwa a cikin kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ta nuna cewa akwai irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen da ke da iyakar kasuwanci a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom, kuma yana tabbatar da cewa COVID-19 ya karu da sauri a duk ƙasashe, a matakan daban-daban dangane da ƙasa.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ya kamata ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa su kara shirye-shiryen su don samun ci gaban marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman da kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na 2019, an ruwaito barkewar cutar huhu a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China, wanda har yanzu ba a san dalilin da ya sa ake samun cutar ta yaduwa ba.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar hana cututtuka da kula da cutar ta kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa an gano wani abu da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus mai tsanani, wanda yanzu ake kira cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani, coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Har zuwa yau, akwai shaidu cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke kamuwa da COVID-19 suna kamuwa da cutar huhu, ko da kuwa ba cutar huhu ba, amma suna kamuwa da cututtukan numfashi marasa tsanani, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
A cikin kimanin kashi 14 cikin dari na kamuwa da cutar, COVID-19 ya zama mafi tsanani da ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari na kamuwa da cutar suka sami mummunan cuta da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman.
Kashi na mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu bincika yanayin yiwuwar yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da United Kingdom, kuma mu kwatanta su da lardin Hubei, China, da China.
A cikin shekarar 2020, mun kwatanta adadin cututtukan COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya da adadin cututtukan da ke faruwa a yanzu a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris.
An samu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya
Bayan barkewar cutar a China, COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwa zuwa wasu yankuna, kuma a sauran ƙasashe a duniya, cutar ta COVID-19 ta tashi da sauri.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, babban darektan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Jaridar likita Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al., ta bayyana cewa a ranar 5 ga Maris, an tabbatar da fashewar COVID-19 ta farko a cikin Turai, bisa ga ma'anar barkewar cutar ta WHO.
Mutane uku na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar a cikin EU/EEA an gano su a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma sun dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da kuma United Kingdom (UK), inda aka ba da rahoton kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, da kuma kamuwa da cutar 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a cikin ƙasar Italiya.
Samun adadin adadin yaduwar COVID-19 da yawan yaduwar cutar
Cibiyar Tarayya da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana sabunta bayanan COVID-19 daga ma'aikatun lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da kuma daga kafofin hukuma kamar WHO a kowace safiya da karfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yiwuwar yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta yanayin ƙasashensu da yanayin Italiya.
A matsayin misali na sake fasalin abubuwan da ke faruwa na COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya a cikin kwanaki 14 na gaba da kuma bayan haka, a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, mun lissafa adadin sake fasalin abubuwan da ke faruwa na COVID-19 kuma mun ɗauka cewa adadin COVID-19 na yau da kullun ne.
Mun kuma nuna adadin cututtukan da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da adadin cututtukan da aka ruwaito a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya
Kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun yi daidai da yadda suka yi a lardin Hubei (China) a yau (Figure 1).
Idan aka haɗa dukkan EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu, ƙimar sake fasalin COVID-19 ta fara tashi, sannan ta tashi sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (a cikin ƙarin labarin).
Wannan yafi faruwa ne saboda karuwar yawan adadin kamuwa da cutar da aka samu daga Italiya, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa akwai karuwar adadin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da kuma a cikin Burtaniya (bayanai na gaba).
Hoton 2 ya kwatanta yawan karuwar kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 da lambobin Italiya.
A cikin makonni 3 da kasa, kasashe 15 na Ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Birtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin cututtuka a Italiya a karfe 8:00 na safe, 15 ga Maris.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Bayanan da aka lura da ci gaban COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar ta tashi a daidai wannan matakin a duk ƙasashe.
A cikin ƙasashe, ayyukan kula da cututtukan lafiyar jama'a na kasa suna kan matakai daban-daban, a yanayi daban-daban, kuma har yanzu akwai bambance-bambance tsakanin ƙasashe a cikin hanyoyin da za a zaɓa don bincika marasa lafiya don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da ƙayyadaddun fasalin fashewa da gwajin haɗuwa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke da cutar ta COVID-19 sun bayyana cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin dari na marasa lafiya da ke da cutar suna buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun bayyana cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a yankunan sun kai matakin karɓar marasa lafiya mafi girma.
A cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA), kashi 6% da 1% na yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke asibitoci da dakunan shan magani na musamman suna samuwa (ba a bayyana bayanai ba).
Amma, ya kamata a yi bincike a tsari don ƙarfafa saka idanu na yanzu, wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan marasa lafiya da mutuwar da aka ruwaito.
Wani bincike a 2010-11 ya nuna cewa yawan gadaje na gaggawa da na gaggawa a Turai ya bambanta sosai a kowace ƙasa, inda a Jamus akwai gadaje 29.2 ga kowane 100,000 mazauna, amma a Portugal akwai gadaje 4.2 kawai.
Wannan yana nufin cewa Italiya (wanda a shekara ta 2010-11 ya kai 12.5 a cikin mutane 100,000 da ke da wuraren da za a iya ba da kulawa ta musamman da kuma matsakaiciyar kulawa) suna da albarkatu da yawa fiye da Italiya, kuma suna iya samun ƙasa da yawa.
An haɗa ƙididdigar yanayin tunanin mutum da ke tattare da cika adadin kulawar lafiya da ke dacewa da haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin COVID-19 na asibiti wanda ya fi 90% haɗarin da ke tattare da yawan wuraren da za a iya kula da su a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya, tare da ƙididdigar sake kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 na asibiti a cikin ECDC ta Saurin Gyara na takwas na gwajin haɗarin COVID-19.
A wasu yankuna na EU / EEA da Burtaniya, cutar ta bazu sosai kuma asibitoci da wuraren kulawa na musamman galibi suna iya magance yawan jama'a na gida, saboda haka, ya kamata a ba da bayanai game da barkewar cutar da yawan wuraren kula da marasa lafiya zuwa cibiyoyin gida don samun bayanan lamba na Level 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar da aka samu daga Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Duk da haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da wuraren kulawa ta gaggawa ya kamata su yi shiri a gaba don sarrafa kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin yankin da kuma karuwar yawan mutanen COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa ta gaggawa, kamar yadda lamarin ya faru a yankunan da cutar ke fama da ita a Italiya.
Kamar yadda ECDC ta kwanan nan ta nuna a cikin ƙididdigar haɗarin gaggawa, don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2 yana buƙatar saurin, ingantaccen, ingantaccen tsarin rigakafin cutar tare da hanyar sauyawa daga sarrafawa zuwa ragewa. Idan adadin marasa lafiya ya karu da sauri kamar yadda aka zata, rashin shirye-shirye na iya haifar da rashin isasshen lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don fahimtar yanayin cutar da kuma amsawa yadda ya kamata.
A cikin saurin tantance haɗarin, an kuma ba da shawarar matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage cutar.
Kasashe suna da damar gajeren lokaci don ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba akan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba a cimma wannan ba, tsarin kula da lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU / EEA na iya fuskantar karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) wanda ya haifar da cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 (Covid-2), ta haifar da bala'i ga mutane, inda ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya har zuwa yanzu, kuma ya kai fiye da 80,000.
Kamar SARS-CoV-2 wanda ya haifar da cutar SARS-CoV a cikin dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar daga ƙwayoyin cuta kuma yana iya haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ta hanyar haɗin haɗin haɗin gwiwa.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin haɗari da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da ƙarancin yaduwa kuma yana ɗaukar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
A cikin martani ga yawan wallafe-wallafen da ake yi game da cutar, an yi ƙoƙari don samar da cikakken bayani game da batutuwan bincike masu saurin ci gaba a cikin lokaci.
Za mu yi aiki tare don nazarin cutar, nazarin abubuwan da ke haifar da cutar, nazarin cutar, ganowa, magani, bincike da rigakafi.
Ko da yake har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ake bukatar amsoshi, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar cutar da ke barazana kuma ya taimaka wajen kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020, ya zama abin tunawa ga duk 'yan kasar Sin da aka ƙarfafa su zauna a gida a lokacin hutu da kuma makonni bayan hutu saboda barkewar cutar kwayar cutar.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2 saboda irin kamanceceniya da cutar ta coronavirus (CoV), wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a shekara ta 2003.
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa kasar Sin da kusan kasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da aka tabbatar da sama da mutane 80,000, fiye da 40,000 sun bar asibiti, kuma fiye da 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 ita ce babbar magabcin jama'a kuma tana da ƙarfi fiye da ta'addanci.
A cikin watanni biyu bayan da aka gudanar da rahoton farko na bincike kan sarkar cutar, a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020, bayan da aka bayyana a PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), an buga fiye da takardu 200 game da COVID-19 dangane da nazarin cutar, nazarin annobar, nazarin dalilin cutar, bincike da magani.
Wannan bita na nufin taƙaita bincike akan sabon yanki na abun ciki wanda ke canzawa cikin sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi ƙoƙari mu kwatanta COVID-19 da cututtukan da ke tattare da SARS da sauran CoV, cuta ta hanyar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (matsanancin cutar MERS a shekara ta 2012).
Za mu tattauna duk abin da muka sani, da kuma yadda za a hana cutar da kuma gano ta a gaba, da kuma wasu batutuwa na gaggawa da suka rage.
CoVs sune abubuwa masu haifar da cututtuka waɗanda ba su da haɗari ga mutum, kuma suna haifar da kimanin 15% na yanayin sanyi na 4.
A cikin wannan karni, duk da haka, mun ga cututtukan CoV masu haɗari a cikin mutane sau biyu: SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya fara a 2003 (China) da China da Saudi Arabia a 2012 kuma nan da nan ya bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da mummunan kamuwa da cututtuka da mutuwar.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annoba ta uku ta CoV a tarihin ɗan adam.
An fara bayar da rahoton wani babban yaduwar cutar mura ta huhu a Wuhan ga Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar Sin a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto na 1.1.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an bayyana halin da ake ciki na CoV.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an ruwaito cewa an samu mutuwar farko a birnin Wuhan.
A lokacin, cutar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa, jihohi da ƙasashe masu iyaka.
