A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Gwamnatin Amurka ta sanar da cewa sun ci gaba da samar da kayan aikin gwaji na kansu.
A lokacin da aka yi wannan aikin, sai dai Amurka ta yi jinkiri wajen gudanar da gwajin, saboda haka, ya yi wuya a san halin da cutar ke ciki a lokacin.
Gwajin ya zama ba shi da tasiri saboda ɓarnar kayan aikin gwaji da gwamnatin tarayya ta bayar a watan Fabrairu. Ƙungiyoyin da ba na gwamnati ba (masana, makarantu, jami'o'i) ba su ba da izinin gwajin na tarayya ba har zuwa ƙarshen Fabrairu, saboda haka ana buƙatar jama'a su shiga cikin ƙa'idodin don yin gwajin har zuwa farkon Maris (kuma ana buƙatar amincewar likita).
A ranar 27 ga watan Fabrairu, Washington Post ta ruwaito cewa, a Amurka, an yi gwajin gwaji kasa da 4,000.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, jaridar The Atlantic ta ruwaito cewa an kammala gwajin kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, EPA ta ba da rahoton cewa mutane da yawa da ke da alamun cutar sun jira sa'o'i ko kwanaki kafin a gwada su. Bayan mutuwar farko a Amurka, a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya sanar da dokar ta baci a Washington, wanda wasu jihohi suka bi.
Makarantun da ke yankin Seattle sun soke darussan a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, an rufe makarantun a duk faɗin ƙasar. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, ƙungiyar masu ilimin cututtukan cututtuka a Kwalejin Inperial ta London ta ba da shawarar ga Amurka game da ƙididdigar tasirin sabon coronavirus a kan ƙasa.
A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya rattaba hannu kan Dokar Shirya da Saurin Amsawa da ke Kula da Korona, wanda ya ba da dala biliyan 8.3 don kudade na gaggawa ga hukumomin tarayya don amsawa ga barkewar cutar.
